      "author_association" : "MEMBER",
      "body" : "I would suggest using a lower -dbcache setting on 32-bit systems (all Bitcoin released binaries for Windows are 32-bit). It's quite likely you're just running out of address space (between 2 and 3 GB for 32-bit processes, IIRC).\n",
